        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"Laminin α5 Is Deposited at Synapses by Hippocampal Neurons\"\n- \"Hippocampal Neurons Deposit the ECM Protein Laminin α5 at Synapses\"\n- \"Laminin α5 Is Delivered by the Postsynaptic Neuron\"\n\n9/7/2018 Pim\n- Laminin is a known component of the ECM.. Experimental description: - \"Conditional allele Lama5 mice (Nguyen et al., 2005) ...\"\n- Species of overexpressed Laminin alpha5 is not stated in the paper." ;
